Well today i had my walk-a-thon but as it was forrcasted rain it got changed to a fun-a-thon.. and as yr 12 is such a great bunch we ran the activities, i was doing Triva, 6 of us were spilt into 3 room to organise this event,  and i did 6 sessions of this.. its a good thing i dont want to be a teacher anymore because it totally turned me off!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! hehe i was so totally bored as.  

each year group had a different theme to dress up as, yr 12 was the 80s.. it was pretty funnny some of the diff clothes ppl wore..  mine was pretty plain due to the late notice!! but i still looked good!! 

my mum boke her toe when gettin ready for my party the other day, but only saw a doctor today, she just has to keep off it, but impossible for my mum, shes hopeless, which reminds me i have to go do the washin.. ill continue this later..

xox

Although i only have 2 periods today so i finish at 10.35 i think, then im off to penrith to go to work, even though i dont start till 1.30pm. Im pretty excited to work at the moment as i have a major crush on a girl i work with.. she's straightso i know nothing will ever happen, she knows i like her, but everything is still relitively normal,its just hard when trying not to stare at her much, as she is beautiful and full of life, even though she is at Wendys every single day, while waiting to start uni next year.. 
umm i think its like 5 days till my bday of smtg like dat, yay go the 29th of August!!!!!!!!! 
ahhh ya i won at basketball last night, and i actually played alright got the two shots that i tried i got in.. thats something that doesnt happpen all that often.. 
oh yes in my last entry i said i failed 3 out of 5 exams, new developents since then, my teacher counted up my marks wrong so i got 58% instead of 48% in food tec in was great!!!!
still pretty pooor but atleast i passed, anyway i think the lesson is about to end so love you all... bubye xoxox

i failed 3 out of 5 trial exams, even food tec which i tried so hard for, i got that back today i was soooooooooo upset. im a bit scared of telling mum, i dont want her to be disapointed in me, which i know she will be... 

mmmm i dont think theres much new with me, my life consists of school and work, i never get to see any of my friends that mean the world to me.. 

im trying this new thing where im trying to be confident with myself and be comfortable with who i am.. so some of u may know already, but i like girls.. i guess im bi, as i still like guys.. so there ive said it now, oh ya no one tell my family!!! oh and ally if u read this then plz dont mention this at school as the trouble it caused last term, i spent most of that term paranoid and angry at people who i thought were my friends, ha ya right... the things people come up with and i hadnt even said anything, i can only imagine if i did say smtg... 

ya i think thats all ill say atm

*hugs* sarah xoxo

well omg its 2006, the year i graduate... how scary does that sound... now that christmas has past(which was offically crap) and ive been to melbourne which was great, i had a fab time. as well as the new year in which i feel asleep on my 2nd cousins lounge room floor while being terrised by his kids.. i get back in which i have to work the next 5 days... grrr and i have soooo much work to do, with no time to do it... and to topo it off ive decided to change my irp topic for cfs, with 6 wks left to do it in.. and am feeling like shit atm for a number of reasons which i wont bore u with.

2005 in review!!!!!
-started yr 11
-started working at wendys
-fell in love then back out of, then back in(vishes circle)
-first proper bf
-first kiss according to mum.. lol

oh well gtg clean the house 4 mummy

ya its really hot in this room so im going... i hope everyone has a great christmas... and doesnt forgot the real reason we celerbrate the day... much love to everyone... xoxoxoxoxoxoxoxoxoxoxoxoxoxoxoxo

hmmm well im in my study for today and you can see im not getting alot of work done, tho i did type out my questionaire, and im thinking of putting on my lj, so anyone who wants to can fill it in, and it would be a great help for me.. yesterday was my last uni exam, so ive finished the unit on humam development, i know i passed with out the exam so im pretty happy, tho i dont think i will get a credit as only 20% of the 60ish get it, so thats a bit disapointing. ive been in a weird mood lately, one day im soooo very happy like in my entry on friday, and by the next day im totally the oposite, there are reasons but its just to hard to explain atm as id have to start at the very begining... m
mum went to hospital on sunday, as when she was mowing on the ride on lawn mower at jamies, and its on a hill, and somehow she fell off, the mower fell on her and punched her leg, its on her shin, so they cant stitch it up as there is no skin to spare on da shin, i dunno, theres like this hole in her leg about an inch deep.. eww its gross, i have a picture but its on my phone and i dont know how to get on on the computer... she was ment to come out yesterday but she had to have minor surgey, to clean it out properly, as its open and she was cutting lawn at the time. but all in all she ok! i just miss her atm. 
Today is tuesday, which means after today there is 3 more days of school, oh i sooooo cant wait fo the holidays, more free time to hang out with friends ;-) but at the moment im so exusted, i need alot of sleep, many hours to catch up and get rid of the dark cirles under my eyes... 
oh and im going to melbourne on the 27th for 7 days with my great aunty barb, to go down to see her son, who she only met last year, im excited, i need to get away. 
and im sorry to those of u ive ignored of not paid attention to in the last couple of months, as ive been really really stressed out.. but its all good atm.. oh ya nat if u read this i love u so very much, ur the bestest chicken eva, and we need to reall catch up, u too lou, we need to catch up to and everyone else i havent seen in ages.. much love to u all 
xxxSarahxxx :-) :-)
